Scrapy
    - comes with its own API
    - makes it easy to write and debug spiders
    - can run it on the command line or jupyter


- Not a good idea to use regular expressions to pick out what you want on the html page
    - regex ignores context


- Auto-throttle
    - dynamically sets delay based on how quickly server responds

- caching
    - to avoid hammering the server, used a cached version of the website

- robots.txt file
    - tells you what kind of activities you can engage in
